Madelyn Clare https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Madelyn_Clare 0 Madelyn Clare (18 November 1894 – 20 September 1975; also known as Madelyn Klare or Madelyn Donovan) was an American actress during the early twentieth century. Born in Cleveland, Ohio, she was married to writer and director Thomas Dixon Jr.. She died in Raleigh, North Carolina.
